
This is a merge of the openexr_ctl and ctl projects. The 'openexr_ctl'
project has become the openexr directory. Note that over time the utilities
that were in those locations are getting moved *out* an into this top level
directory.

There will also be the addition of a number of sample ctl 'scripts' into
this directory (which will start out quite confused until they are all
sorted out and documented).
